ZH: 1. 我的水壶是粉色的。
EN: My water bottle is pink.
ZH: 2. 这个水壶可以装满一升水。
EN: This water bottle can hold one liter of water.
ZH: 3. 我的水壶丢失了，我得去买一个新的。
EN: I lost my water bottle, I need to buy a new one.
ZH: 4. 这个水壶还带有一个便携式杯子。
EN: This water bottle also comes with a portable cup.
ZH: 5. 我喜欢用不锈钢水壶装咖啡。
EN: I like to use a stainless steel water bottle to carry coffee.
ZH: 6. 我的水壶有个保温功能，可以保持水温很久。
EN: My water bottle has a thermal insulation function, it can keep the water temperature for a long time.
ZH: 7. 你的水壶看起来很漂亮。
EN: Your water bottle looks very nice.
ZH: 8. 我的儿子在水壶里装了果汁。
EN: My son put juice in the water bottle.
ZH: 9. 这个水壶特别轻便，很适合户外活动。
EN: This water bottle is very lightweight, perfect for outdoor activities.
ZH: 10. 他在山上发现了一个废弃的水壶。
EN: He found an abandoned water bottle on the mountain.
ZH: 11. 我在超市里买了一个新的水壶。
EN: I bought a new water bottle at the supermarket.
ZH: 12. 她把水壶里的水都喝光了。
EN: She drank all the water in the water bottle.
ZH: 13. 这个不锈钢水壶很耐用，可以使用很长时间。
EN: This stainless steel water bottle is very durable and can be used for a long time.
ZH: 14. 我的朋友送我一个漂亮的玻璃水壶。
EN: My friend gave me a beautiful glass water bottle.
ZH: 15. 我的水壶上贴满了贴纸。
EN: My water bottle is covered with stickers.
ZH: 16. 这个水壶有一个可拆卸的过滤器。
EN: This water bottle has a removable filter.
ZH: 17. 我把水壶装在背包里方便携带。
EN: I put the water bottle in the backpack for easy carrying.
ZH: 18. 他很在意他的水壶颜色是否能与背包相匹配。
EN: He cares about whether the color of his water bottle can match the backpack.
ZH: 19. 这个水壶设计得非常精巧。
EN: This water bottle is designed very delicately.
ZH: 20. 我带了一个水壶去登山。
EN: I brought a water bottle for hiking.
